sudo apt update
sudo apt search keyword (like bluetooth)
sudo apt install app name

/etc/apt/sources.list -> you can add repositories for multiple distros

sudo apt remove app name -> can leave behind conf files
sudo apt purge app name -> gets rid of everything connected to the app


Getting tools from GitHub
sudo git clone https://github.com/repository name

Necessary tools:
- mousepad
- pip - sudo apt install python3-pip
- shodan - sudo pip3 install shodan:
	shodan init api-key
	shodan search port: 502	country:fr
- sudo gem install modbus-cli -> gem is a ruby package manager


